{"tid":1707983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動策略]千其千其唔好再亂set Road Block","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:52:54.000Z","uid":148795,"like":99,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"01c2e0ff586d53785895b671a5eb1194f1774d42","tid":1707983,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"你地繼續一字排開咁set road block好啦<br />\n咁樣我呢啲上班一族先有機會落車清road block<br />\n千其唔好好似隔離po所講留返一條線比車行啊<br />\n不過其實留一條線啲車龍都清得好快所以我呢個超級藍絲係唔會驚你地嘅<br />\n但係求下你地千其千其唔好好似下圖咁set road block<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmijHR2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmijHR2.jpg&h=fe03d027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一陣你地set到啲rb好似迷宮咁逼啲司機減慢哂車速咁去行<br />\n如果你地真係set都唔該2個rb個距離set近啲啊<br />\n太近啲車轉唔到線咁我呢個超級藍絲又有機會落車清走你啲rb了<br />\n但係如果架車一路keep住慢慢行我又無藉口落車清rb咁就仆街了實遲到"},{"pid":"64bfd29e65b198dfd9d066c3608c7da54d9e8b59","tid":1707983,"uid":148795,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:30:37.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續落車清rb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11089f9f2aa7e102c3e5f7c5a07272de769cc365","tid":1707983,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"7fb07dbcebc150fa799498540ec03725a8d637cd","tid":1707983,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:31:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"108f4341792174d708c11d33fce2fda8fe92004e","tid":1707983,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ade126de6a69aba617e20204848e569c1cdc12e0","tid":1707983,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"無人入嚟"},{"pid":"54829e6ccee7dd2f2248eb3d18afdb31e00a3341","tid":1707983,"uid":197734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"咁樣應該要搬走都依然好易?"},{"pid":"f7e1fb119b956a9b7